            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>harissa paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and<strong> tomato paste</strong> in a bowl with your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> – this is your<strong> harissa mix</strong></p><p>Pat your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Top each <strong>pastry rectangle</strong> with a <strong>basa fillet</strong>, covering only one half</p><p>Spoon the <strong>harissa mix</strong> evenly over the basa</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1684849467635-x200.jpg",
